{"type": "article", "id": 22323, "title": "纽扣象棋", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-16T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607111734oLCQ2kVXSEdvz31T.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一套很有手工感的象棋，是胡桃木做的。每一颗象棋像小的纽扣，用深浅两色来区分。棋盘上使用激光蚀刻的技术，在需要加深的区域刻上密集的弧形波纹，使棋盘既有原本的木纹，也能做成深浅相间的网格。加拿大设计师 AtelierDmontreal 手工做出这套象棋，售价 150 加元，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/ca/listing/263939763/wooden-checkers?ref=shop_home_feat_2\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111732e506Wk4RMfEhaKCt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111732nWyS6rgHqE7IFAJG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111733zdSnvTDVBmsJ8Xf4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111733ULMTDlpu4xBrGyQV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}